title: A Conversation with Mel Martin and Benny Carter.mov
creator: Mel Martin
description: Benny Carter and Mel Martin talked about Benny's remarkable life in Jazz before their appearance at the 1993 San Francisco Jazz Festival. In celebration of Benny's Centennial, please check out their collaboration live at Yoshi's, "Just Friends." For more info, please visit: http://www.melmartin.com and http://www.jazzalleytv.com
